===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|botany}} One of the [[component]]s of a [[compound leaf]].
# {{lb|en|botany}} A [[small]] [[plant]] [[leaf]].
#: {{ux|en|The new '''leaflets''' at the end of the branch were a lighter shade of green than the mature leaves.}}
#: {{syn|en|leafling}}
# A small [[sheet]] of [[paper]] containing [[information]], used for [[dissemination]] of said information, often an [[advertisement]].
#: {{syn|en|flyer|folder|handbill|pamphlet}}
#: {{ux|en|A '''leaflet''' had been left under the car's [[windshield wiper]].}}
# {{lb|en|anatomy}} A [[flap]] of a [[valve]] of a [[heart]] or [[blood vessel]].

